description: 1969-1975. The bands that weren't Sabbath, up until the point Priest sealed the heavy metal sound. Picked for upping the riffs (Purple), tempo (Uriah Heep), image (Cooper), growl (Dio in Elf/Rainbow), or occult lyrics (Coven). Nods to Sam Dunn, and Metallica (still my favorite cover band).
